<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idd3af07a7-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370" identifier="/us/usc/t11/s1162"><num value="1162">§ 1162.</num><heading> Definition</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this subchapter, “Board” means the “Surface Transportation Board”.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idd3af07a8-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/104/88/tIII/s302/1">Pub. L. 104–88, title III, § 302(1)</ref>, <date date="1995-12-29">Dec. 29, 1995</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/109/943">109 Stat. 943</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idd3af07a9-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idd3af07aa-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="idd3af07ab-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior section 1162, <ref href="/us/pl/95/598">Pub. L. 95–598</ref>, <date date="1978-11-06">Nov. 6, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/2641">92 Stat. 2641</ref>, defined “Commission”, prior to repeal by <ref href="/us/pl/104/88/tIII/s302/1">Pub. L. 104–88, title III, § 302(1)</ref>, <date date="1995-12-29">Dec. 29, 1995</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/109/943">109 Stat. 943</ref>.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idd3af07ac-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idd3af07ad-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1996-01-01">Jan. 1, 1996</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/104/88/s2">section 2 of Pub. L. 104–88</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t49/s1301">section 1301 of Title 49</ref>, Transportation.</p>
</note>
